ing on the planets for your loot. To avoid being left with nothing, store some of them in your storage room to be ready for your next expedition.<br> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2715910/extras/c87665761e0c01ecf27e3cb465b61b3e.poster.avif?t=1746697671\" width=768 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2715910/extras/c87665761e0c01ecf27e3cb465b61b3e.webm?t=1746697671\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2715910/extras/c87665761e0c01ecf27e3cb465b61b3e.mp4?t=1746697671\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2715910/extras/57a71ae8ab5b7d688d82f1adc6b5b941.avif?t=1746697671\" width=600 height=100 /></span>Take up the challenge and fight for the loot on the uncharted territories of <strong>a unique planet</strong>, brimming with diverse landscapes, challenging terrains, and protected bases full of precious items. Discover a wealth of resources, hunt, and engage in an intense fight against a <strong>multitude of enemies</strong> each presenting distinct challenges.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2715910/extras/c961d58eca723d13a90d18a834d765b0.poster.avif?t=1746697671\" width=768 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2715910/extras/c961d58eca723d13a90d18a834d765b0.webm?t=1746697671\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2715910/extras/c961d58eca723d13a90d1